_sText:
This is just most basic jailbreak map you will find it has no perks or anything i am leaving that for you to add

i made this for a friend of mine who kept asking me for help on how to start his map

please enjoy this template/prefab
it comes with a cage 5 cells
and armory with weaponspawners
and a yard (empty)

i am including the vmf file that you need to download

please if you post a map using this template as a start please give some credit by posting the link to this in your readme and in the co-creator area
